<h2 class="bold font-l">Roxas, "The Key of Destiny"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Each member of Organization XIII wields power over a specific element (be it classical or esoteric). Being a keyblade wielder and the nobody of Sora, Roxas wields the power of light. </p>
