<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Roxas, "The Key of Destiny"</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Each member of Organization XIII wields power over a specific element (be it classical or esoteric). Being a keyblade wielder and the nobody of Sora, Roxas wields the power of light.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="aa3fqe">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
